root -> row1.stack_ops
root -> row1.arithmetic
root -> row2.comparison
root -> row2.functions
legend: |md
  **Category Prefixes:**
  - `0x00` Control Flow
  - `0x10` Stack Operations  
  - `0x20` Arithmetic
  - `0x30` Comparison
  - `0x40` Functions
| {near: bottom-right}